.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-6::.
City: marseilles, new-york, nizza
The people have 3 different jobs:  analyst, chef, videographer
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, thriller, time-travel
3 different pets are kept: bird, goldfish, horse
1. the person traveling to marseilles is the owner of the bird##1
2. the analyst is on the left or right of the person watching time-travel movies##3
3. the videographer is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
4. the person traveling to marseilles is the owner of the bird##1
5. the person traveling to nizza is on the left or right of the owner of the goldfish##3
6. the person traveling to marseilles is the person watching thriller movies##1
7. the person watching action movies is between the owner of the horse and the chef##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |      3       |
| City          | marseilles | new-york    | nizza  |
| Job           | chef      | analyst  | videographer |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller  | action   | time-travel  |
| Pet           | bird      | goldfish | horse        |

