There 3 different types of food: banana, blueberry, pineapple
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: folk, hip-hop, soul
The people use 3 different means of transport: bike, bus, helicopter
1. the person eating banana is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
2. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the fan of soul##1
3. the fan of folk is on the far right##1
4. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
5. the person watching romance movies is the person eating blueberry##1
6. the person driving the bike is the fan of folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |      3      |
| Movie-Genre      | romance       | disaster | epic |
| Food          | blueberry  | banana | pineapple   |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop    | soul   | folk        |
| Transport     | helicopter | bus    | bike        |

