The people's birthday is in 3 different months: october, february, may
3 different pets are kept: cat, rat, turtle
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: basketball, cycling, handball
1. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
2. the owner of the cat is on the far left##1
3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
4. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
5. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3
6. the person who's sport is handball is the person watching romance movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |
| Movie-Genre   | satire     | fantasy   | romance   |
| Birthday   | february   | may | october |
| Pet           | cat        | turtle    | rat       |
| Sport         | basketball | cycling   | handball  |

