3. the person who growssunflower is between the owner of the fish and the person eating garlic##2
4. the person who growsazalea is on the far right##1
5. the person eating garlic is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
6. the person who growsazalea is on the left or right of the person eating peach##3
7. the person eating garlic is the person driving the bus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Food        | garlic       | peach     | cucumber   |
| Pet         | dog          | lizard    | fish       |
| Flower       | marigold | sunflower | azalea |
