.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, juice, mirinda
There are 3 different favourite colors: brown, turquise, lavender
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: animation, comedy, fantasy
3 different pets are kept: ferret, horse, turtle
1. the person who likes lavender is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
2. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
3. the owner of the horse is on the far right##1
4. the person who likes brown is on the far left##1
5. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left or right of the person watching comedy movies##3
6. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person watching comedy movies##3
7. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
8. the person watching comedy movies is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |       3       |
| Beverage      | mirinda | juice  | hot-chocolate |
| Color           | brown  | lavender  | turquise      |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy | comedy | animation     |
| Pet           | turtle  | ferret | horse         |

 